description:
Constructor options for HttpConnector — REST polling adapter. Source: packages/connector-http/src/HttpConnector.ts.

Protocol:
• GET  {url}/messages?cursor=...  — { messages: IncomingMessage[], cursor?: string }
• POST {url}/messages             — Body: OutgoingMessage. Response body ignored.
• POST {url}/survey               — Body: SurveyPayload. Response body ignored.
• GET  {url}/history?cursor=...   — Optional. { messages, hasMore, cursor? }
